<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Eden chulnung pakthing bang alun kit nan,
 Khawvel hukhing din Lengmang a pieng;
 Pielgal nunnawp puon bang I silh theihna din,
 Pathien cha'n mun nuoinungpen A hun tel tai.

[V2]
 Lampak hitiu, Vawnchawih hung piengpa chu,
 Chawih-atna'n lam bangin pak hitiu;
 Ziebang lawma ei dinga Leng hung pieng chu,
 A pieng puou pieng kit ta puona kumsawtin.

[V3]
 2. Malai miten muh a nawpuh zie ni hi,
 Mu loin sang tamtak muolliem zo,
 Chung Pathien Vawnchawih nausena A pienni,
 Tulai mi'n gobang I chan I hampha ngei.

[V4]
 3. Tuma, tunung vannuoia minsak lakah,
 Hukdampa bang kuomah pieng puon au;
 Malai mi thiengtho Simeon tawbanga,
 Mu-a kipak cheng mi hampha pen a hiu.

[V5]
 4. Lei leh vana simsen loh mipi lakah,
 A pha chungchuong pen ie Hukdampa;
 Israel te'n mang banga apaih nunguh,
 Chung Lengmang, Minlun go bangin ka vawp tai.</lyrics>
<title>Lampak hitiu</title>
<hymn_number>6</hymn_number>
</song>